      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOT IMMUNITY (4) has been in sparkling form, last time showing brilliant early pace and proving too slick around this track over 400m in 23.11, making it three wins on end. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with five wins from 12 starts. Expected to go well again. SMOOTH TIGER (6) was narrowly beaten last time, jumping from this same box when a 0.7 lengths second in a Grade 5 over 400m at this track. Has the ability and looks a key chance. WEIRD KAREN (2) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 12 from 25 starts. Finished in the minors last time when third (23.14) at this track making it back to back placings. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Will give a great sight again. TERRORISING TOM (8) can feature with the right run.",
